ğŸ Backend Setup:

a. Create Django project
    mkdir backend && cd backend
    python -m venv venv
    source venv/bin/activate
    pip install django djangorestframework openai (pip install django djangorestframework google-generativeai)
    django-admin startproject job_applier .

ğŸ’š Frontend Setup:

b. Create Vue project
    cd ../frontend
    npm create vue@latest vue-app
    cd vue-app
    npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/vite
    # npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer


c. Set environment variables

    Create a .env file in the root directory with the following content:

   export OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key
   export GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key

ğŸš€ Run the app

    docker compose up --build
